(13889, 'butalbital, acetaminophen and caffeine', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Butalbital, Acetaminophen and Caffeine Tablets may enhance the effects of: other narcotic analgesics, alcohol, general anesthetics, tranquilizers such as chlordiazepoxide, sedative-hypnotics, or other CNS depressants, causing increased CNS depression', 'DailyMed'),
