(13889, 'butalbital, aspirin and caffeine', 'N/A', 'minor', 'Drug Interactions: Patients receiving narcotic analgesics, antipsychotics, antianxiety agents, or other CNS depressants (including alcohol) concomitantly with Butalbital, Aspirin, and Caffeine Tablets may exhibit additive CNS depressant effects.', 'DailyMed'),
