(19059, 'terbinafine', 'N/A', 'minor', '7 DRUG INTERACTIONS Terbinafine is an inhibitor of CYP4502D6 isozyme and has an effect on metabolism of desipramine, cimetidine, fluconazole, cyclosporine, rifampin, and caffeine. Terbinafine decreases the clearance of caffeine by 19%.', 'DailyMed'),
