(19288, 'quinidine sulfate tablet', 'N/A', 'major', 'Conversely, the pharmacokinetics of quinidine are not significantly affected by caffeine, ciprofloxacin, digoxin, diltiazem, felodipine, omeprazole, or quinine.', 'DailyMed'),
